      "edited_at": "2026-04-15T15:28:51.881Z",
      "content": "<p>On my stance towards the role of automation in work applications:</p><p><a href=\"https://arttuv.com/writings/automation-and-the-role-of-human-operators/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">arttuv.com/writings/automation</span><span class=\"invisible\">-and-the-role-of-human-operators/</span></a></p><p>I think we should try to keep humans as active participants in work whenever possible, unless the work is so trivial we can fully automate it.</p>",
